    <keyword>adj-rib-out</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The BGP Monitoring Protocol (BMP) only defines access to the Adj-RIB-In Routing Information Bases (RIBs).  This document updates BMP (RFC 7854) by adding access to the Adj-RIB-Out RIBs.  It also adds a new flag to the peer header to distinguish between Adj-RIB-In and Adj-RIB-Out.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
